After many years of searching for the right publisher for @ketolikeachef  we have finally partnered with 
@girlfridayproductions to launch this book for Spring of 2024. Finding the right publisher was such a challenge, but @keithschikore and I are so so excited to share our covid project with the world. Please please please pre-order the book when it goes on sale to help make this book a best-seller and get into the all-mighty algorithm. Much love to everyone involved.

We are ok. Everything is totaled in Lahaina. I lost my home and everything besides my passport and our lives. Anything helps right now and we are just lucky to escape on a dirt bike road at the right time. People burned in their cars, drowned jumping off buildings. This is a huge tragedy and we are in shock.
We are starting back up the Chef Collective to help feed people in the upcoming months. Link is in my bio to donate. Anything is appreciated
Please donate and help us rebuild and feed people in need. Links in my bio

We are partnered with Hua Momona Farms 501c3 and are organizing efforts. We have a Refrigerated Truck, Huge Fridge Space, and a Food Truck to work out of the next couple months north of Lahaina. Links are in my Bio. Please pass along to any major donors. This will be our work for the foreseeable future.
Hua Momona Farms and I are partnered and looking for more donors to help support for the next year. Mauifirechefcollective.com and links in my bio
Raising money with Cheeseburgers! Come to @missionstburgers and help support @outsidelands meat and ingredients donated by @allenbrotherssteaks  and @chefswarehouse
Palo Alto News. I am flying back to Lahaina Thursday to work with @huamomonafoundation for the next upcoming months. Please reach out if you’d like to contribute or help in any way.

@hhhmaui Coming in Hot. This team is 600 Strong of Badass MF’s helping with food sustainability in Maui. We’ve been partners for years @huamomonafoundation and they are our network of endless distribution. Come help us make some delicious food @huamomonafarms and spread some Aloha. Ramping up meals over the next few weeks to meet demands. 🤘

Rosemary Seared Chicken, Feta Dressing, Greek Nuac Cham Salad, Tumeric Cilantro Rice, @huamomonafarms Micros. We donated 220 of these today and are gonna Beef up our game with some seared Sirloin for at least 350 displaced people in need in Lahaina on Thursday. Come join our journey to 1000 people per day! Pictures to come! Please donate! Link in Bio #LahainaStrong

Pig is on the menu this week. After the loss of the Lahaina Luau there was a surplus of whole pigs in Olowalu, so @huamomonafoundation has been buying them up. We are using a fortified pork stock today to braise 300 lbs of St. Louis Ribs  and using the Meat for a Congee Dish on Monday

We made 660 @mauinuivenison Venison Larb with Vietnamese Vermicelli Mix, Fried Eggplant Salad, Peanut & Crispy Garlic Streusel, & @huamomonafarms Micros  Today lead by the talented @mauigourmetfood & @lokedawg and donated via @hhhmaui Come to the farm and cook with us every day 8 am - 3 pm! Thank you to all the volunteers who make this happen every day. All a huge thanks to @mauinuivenison for the donated delicious Venison!!!

750 of these plates went out to the local community today. 750 @mauinuivenison Venison Meatballs with @huamomonafarms Mustard Mix, Cilantro Blossoms, & Quinoa Salad went out to the Maui Community Today. We are up to 12,000 meals since the fires happened. Thanks for all your support!

On September 9, we came together with Chef Jason Raffin and the Lahaina Fires Chef Collective to donate 20% of our lunch and dinner proceeds to assist Chef Raffin in supplying high-quality ingredients to Maui locals affected by the devastating August wildfires.

We're thrilled to share that, with the incredible support of our partners, Gala Restaurant in Aventura, Florida, and The Foundry in Dayton, Ohio, we've reached our goal for this critical mission. To all who dined with us on these special days, we extend our deepest gratitude. Your contributions are helping us make a tangible difference in the lives of those in need.
